{"tid":1839503,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【五戴要求缺一不可】何栢良親身落場戴口罩教學，加送超可愛whatsapp sticker","createTime":"2020-01-24T12:40:25.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-24T13:41:30.000Z","uid":138409,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"2f653968c8635cb12eedf0f02e21b24e9b62d625","tid":1839503,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T12:40:25.000Z","msg":"私人身分做埋政府嗰份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n武漢肺炎向全球擴散，香港不能倖免，市民都驚沙士重臨，但係政府反應超慢，港大感染及傳染病中心總監何栢良昨日係電台節目，批評政府防疫正作連17年前沙士都不如，又唔做防疫宣傳。既然政府唔做，何醫生自己出心出力做，唔單止喺辦公室開youtube做live教市民戴口罩，仲特別拍咗一輯「五戴要求缺一不可」，首集搵朋友一齊係港鐵車廂內拍片，示範好多市民錯誤戴口罩嘅方法，只遮口唔遮鼻，當然最後何醫生出場教大家點樣正確戴口罩。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【全民抗疫】五個高危播毒行為你要知 經常捽眼捽鼻掂口罩好危險<br />\n<br />\n何醫生仲製作多張whatsapp貼圖 ，教大家日常生活防疫貼士，包括用廁所嘅衞生習慣。<br />\n到今時今日政府仲只係識播「止暴制亂」廣告，都唔肯認認真真教市民防疫，大家想知多啲點防疫知識，可以去以下連結聽吓何醫生點教大家:<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/vH6Xv1lAI_Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FvH6Xv1lAI_Y&d=3ovy23W4cNvxoMUnqPf77WWYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=f3bc5d8f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/vH6Xv1lAI_Y</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Z85ZRdJJbj4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FZ85ZRdJJbj4&d=3ovy23W4cNvxoMUnqPf77WWYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=c2f40f30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Z85ZRdJJbj4</a><br />\n<br />\nwhatsapp sticker<br />\n<a href=\"https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.pineappledesign.drhostickerapp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fplay.google.com%2Fstore%2Fapps%2Fdetails%3Fid%3Dcom.pineappledesign.drhostickerapp&d=3ovy23W4cNvxoMUnqPf77WWYsxP5Z0Wle18NOkmjjC4%3D&h=a5da10e1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.pineappledesign.drhostickerapp</a>"},{"pid":"88956f5f34968dc04ee5e8ca8d29c6b90d1b4262","tid":1839503,"uid":138409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-24T12:41:52.00